('29856','deDE','Cairn der Knochen','Benutzt die Meditationskerze am Cairn der Knochen.','Euer Geist war klar.$B$BIhr dachtet, Ihr wret konzentriert.$B$BVielleicht war es das stndige Brummen der Insekten, das Euch einschlafen lie. So muss es gewesen sein!$B$BAus dem Augenwinkel seht Ihr eine weitere Steinformation, genau nrdlich von hier.$B$BVielleicht ist es dort ruhiger...','','','','','','Sprecht mit Ka Pao am Cairn der Knochen.','0'),
('29856','enUS','Cairn of Bone','Use the Meditation Candle at the Cairn of Bone.','Your mind felt clear.$b$bYou thought you were focused.$b$bMaybe it was the droning of the nearby insects that put you to sleep. That must\'ve been it!$b$bOut of the corner of your eye, you see another of the stone formations just north of here.$b$bPerhaps it\'s quieter at that one...','','','','','','Speak to Ka Pao at the Cairn of Bone.','0'),
('29878','esES','Construir una trampa hozen mejor','Recoge 8 mandukas y 8 tarros de cermica intactos del Lago Kittitata.','Hay algo dolorosamente claro. A los hozen les encanta la \"manduka\".$b$bMientras te encontrabas en tu trance meditativo, tu mente recibi imgenes e impresiones dispersas. Ahora, completamente $gdespierto:despierta,, luchas por dotar de sentido a la experiencia.$b$bLos cimientos de un plan absurdo comienzan a tomar forma en tu cabeza. Podra ser suficientemente absurdo para que funcione...','','','','','','','0'),
('29878','frFR','Confectionner un meilleur pige  hozen','Allez chercher 8 Poisseux et 8 Pots en cramique intacts au Lac Kittitata.','Une chose est dsormais sre. Les hozen adorent ce quils appellent leurs poisseux.$b$bLors de votre profonde transe mditative, des images et des impressions parses sont apparues dans votre esprit. Maintenant que vous tes compltement $grveill:rveille,, vous vous efforcez de trouver un sens  vos visions.$b$bLes bribes dun plan absurde commencent  prendre forme dans votre esprit. Il est tellement fou quil pourrait bien fonctionner','','','','','','','0'),
('30234','esES','Quijasaa','Acaba con Quijasaa y devuelve a Ren su bastn.','Quijasaa! A que es brutal? Se me ocurri a m solo, y creo que es muy adecuado. Estuve intentando durante horas recuperar mi bastn de sus fauces, pero no hubo manera!$B$BBueno, vale... fueron ms bien unos segundos. Prefiero ser sincero con mis amigos, aunque eso haga que mis historias sean mucho ms aburridas.$B$BEn fin, seras tan amable de desatar tu increble furia sobre este crocolisco de extraordinarias fauces, y traerme mi bastn? A poder ser, intacto!','','','','','','Vuelve con: Ren Lengua gnea. Zona: Lago Ptalo Nveo, Valle de la Flor Eterna.','0'),
('30234','frFR','Mchevice','Tuez Mchevice et rendez son Bton long  Ren.','Mchevice! Cest un nom qui fait trembler deffroi, non? Cest moi qui lai baptis ainsi, je trouve que ce nom lui va trs bien. Cela fait des heures que jessaie de lui reprendre mon bton, mais il ne veut pas lcher prise!$B$BBon, daccord, a ne fait que quelques secondes, je naime pas mentir  mes amis, mme si du coup, mes histoires sont plutt barbantes.$B$BEnfin Auriez-vous lamabilit de dchaner votre si puissante rage sur ce crocilisque  la mchoire si vile et me rapporter mon bton? Intact, si possible!','','','','','','Retournez voir Ren Langue de Feu au Lac Blanc-Ptale dans le Val de lternel printemps.','0'),
('30235','enUS','Quid Pro Quo','Defeat Quid, the Spirit of the Misty Falls.','Quid is a very powerful and very ancient water spirit, though you might not know it with his child-like ways.$B$BThis morning, Quid nearly killed several villagers in the bar when he jokingly caused several of the water kegs to explode.$B$BAs long as the water flows, Quid will remain. He cannot be slain. But he can be reminded that we do not take his dangerous antics in jest.$B$BWould you be willing to carry this message to him on behalf of the village?','','','','','','Return to Che Wildwalker at Mistfall Village in the Vale of Eternal Blossoms.','0'),
('30248','enUS','The Butcher','Kill Bai-Jin the Butcher.','Scouts reports place the displaced Shao-Tien Imperion at the north end of the wall.$B$BAngi Autumnlight spelled out your goal in no uncertain terms: find this leader and kill him.','','','','','','Return to Kun Autumnlight at the Setting Sun Garrison in the Vale of Eternal Blossoms.','0'),
('30298','deDE','Die Ruinen in Blut trnken','Ttet 8 Mogu in den Guo-Lai-Ruinen.','Die Mogu denken, sie knnen diese Ruinen ungeschoren bernehmen. Wir wollen ihnen zeigen, dass sie sich irren.','','','','','','Kehrt zu Leven Morgenklinge in den Guo-Lai-Ruinen im Tal der Ewigen Blten zurck.','0'),
('30298','enUS','Painting the Ruins Red','Kill 8 mogu in the Ruins of Guo-Lai.','The mogu think they can inhabit these ruins uncontested. Let\'s show them the error in their ways.','','','','','','Return to Leven Dawnblade at the Ruins of Guo-Lai in the Vale of Eternal Blossoms.','0'),
('30299','deDE','Kein Stein auf dem anderen lassen','Zerstrt 6 Mogustatuen.','Die Mogu haben Seelen mit Gewalt in alte Statuen verpflanzt, um sie zum Leben zu erwecken, zu kontrollieren und sie gegen uns einzusetzen.$B$BDiese gebundenen Geister knnen nur befreit werden, indem man ihre Behltnisse zerstrt.','','','','','','Kehrt zu Sun Zartherz in den Guo-Lai-Ruinen im Tal der Ewigen Blten zurck.','0'),
('30300','enUS','The Key to Success','Find a Shao-Tien Cage Key and free 6 Golden Lotus Prisoners.','The mogu have taken prisoners. They\'ll be tortured or worse.$B$BFind any way you can to free them from their cages.','','','','','','Return to Sun Tenderheart at the Ruins of Guo-Lai in the Vale of Eternal Blossoms.','0'),
('30301','enUS','Offering a Warm Welcome','Burn 6 Mogu Tents in the Ruins of Guo-Lai.','There is no more sure message we can send them then to burn the tents the sleep in.$B$BScour the ruins. Destroy every tent you find.','','','','','','Return to Leven Dawnblade at the Ruins of Guo-Lai in the Vale of Eternal Blossoms.','0'),
('30481','deDE','In Stein gemeielt','Sammelt 12 Guo-Lai-Runensteine zusammen.','Ihr seht Glitzersteine in Mauern? Rook will welche. Die Mogu haben sie auch gesammelt. Vielleicht haben die auch ein paar.$B$BWenn Ihr Steine findet, bringt Ihr sie Rook? Rook wird Euer Freund sein.','','','','','','Kehrt zu Rook Steinzeh in den Guo-Lai-Ruinen im Tal der Ewigen Blten zurck.','0'),
('30481','enUS','Carved in Stone','Collect 12 Guo-Lai Runestones.','You see the shiny stones in the walls? Rook wants some. The mogu been collecting them, so they have some to take too maybe.$B$BIf you find stones, you please bring them to Rook? Rook will be your friend.','','','','','','Return to Rook Stonetoe at the Ruins of Guo-Lai in the Vale of Eternal Blossoms.','0'),
('31244','enUS','Guo-Lai Encampment','Speak to Leven Dawnblade at the Ruins of Guo-Lai.','Leven came by in quite a huff! Said something about mogu in the ruins.$B$BBest be off to find him I think. Angry Leven is not a fun Leven.','','','','','','','0'),
('31246','enUS','Attack on Mistfall Village','Speak to Rook Stonetoe at Mistfall Village.','I can see smoke from the village. And it\'s not my fault this time!$B$BBest go and help.','','','','','','','0'),
('31247','deDE','Die Garnison der Untergehenden Sonne','Sprecht mit Anji Herbstlicht in der Garnison der Untergehenden Sonne.','Anji und Kun haben hier auf dem Weg zur Garnison Rast gemacht. Ein hbsches Paar, findet Ihr nicht? So verschieden und doch so innig miteinander... Ah, wenn ich nur daran denke, geht mir das Herz auf.$B$BSie haben brigens nach Euch gefragt. Vielleicht wollen sie ja, dass Ihr an ein paar Ausbildungseinheiten teilnehmt? Jedenfalls hoffe ich, dass sie nichts Unanstndiges mit Euch vorhaben...','','','','','','','0'),
('31295','enUS','Mogu within the Ruins of Guo-Lai','Speak to Leven Dawnblade at the Ruins of Guo-Lai.','Thank you for your help, $c.$B$BI would enjoy your company for longer, but Leven is leading an attack on the mogu within the Ruins of Guo-Lai to the northwest, and awaits your capable hands.$B$BMay the celestials protect you, young one.','','','','','','','0'),
('32534','enUS','The Skumblade Threat','Slay 10 Skumblade saurok.','Ihgaluk Crag has no end of saurok. Those beasts attack my men and spread their disease into nearby water and wildlife, interfering with our operations.$b$bThin their numbers, $n. Once the Horde takes full control of this island, we can look for more permanent solutions.','','','','','','Return to Archmage Aethas Sunreaver at [TEMP] Horde Town on Mogu Island.','21491'),
('35172','enUS','Your Second Blacksmithing Work Order','Place a work order, then collect it once it completes. $b$bProgress can be monitored through the Garrison Report pane accessible through the button on your minimap.','Place another work order with my assistant. Once it is complete, we will leave it out here for you to collect.','','','','','','Return to the assistant.','0'),
('36810','enUS','[DEPRECATED]Down to Azsuna','Speak with Archmage Khadgar to fly down to Azsuna.','$n, we must find a way to reseal the Tomb of Sargeras.\n\nWhen I was in the Chamber of the Guardian below, I unearthed a tome that spoke of an ancient relic that might be the key to stopping the Legion.\n\nOur search begins here on the ancient elven island of Azsuna. Long ago, it was where the elves of Suramar perfected their mightiest of magics. Now it is a cursed ruins.\n\nI know that the demon hunters of the Illidari have established a camp on the island. Ready to take wing?','','','','','','','21491'),
('36939','deDE','Blut der Annihilan','Besorgt Malinoths Blut.','Wir mssen Kontakt mit dem Geist von Frst Illidan aufnehmen. Aber dazu bentigen wir etwas, das mchtig genug ist, den Nethertiegel anzufeuern. Und ich wei auch schon, was.\n\nEin Grubenlord namens Malinoth hat eine Hhle ganz in der Nhe bernommen. Mit seinem Blut lsst sich der Tiegel anfeuern. Und dann knnt Ihr Kontakt mit Frst Illidan im Wirbelnden Nether aufnehmen.','','','','','','','21287'),
('36939','enUS','Blood of the Annihilan','Collect Malinoth\'s Blood.','We must make contact with Lord Illidan\'s spirit. But to do that, we need something powerful enough to fuel the nether crucible. I know just the thing.\n\nA pit lord named Malinoth has taken over a nearby cave. If we acquire his blood, you can use it to power the crucible. Then, you can make contact with Illidan in the Twisting Nether.','','','','','','','21287'),
('36939','esES','La sangre de los annihilan','Consigue la sangre de Malinoth.','Debemos contactar con el espritu de lord Illidan. Pero para ello necesitamos algo con la potencia suficiente para hacer funcionar el crisol abisal. Y s de algo perfecto.\n\nUn seor del foso llamado Malinoth ha ocupado una cueva cercana. Si conseguimos su sangre, podrs usarla para poner en marcha el crisol y contactar con Illidan en El Vaco Abisal.','','','','','','','21287'),
('36939','frFR','Du sang dAnnihilan','Rcuprez le Sang de Malinoth.','Nous devons entrer en contact avec lesprit du seigneur Illidan. Mais pour ce faire, nous avons besoin dune source dnergie assez puissante pour alimenter le creuset du Nant. Et je sais exactement ce quil nous faut.\n\nUn seigneur des abmes du nom de Malinoth a envahi une grotte voisine. Si nous parvenons  nous procurer de son sang, il nous permettra de faire fonctionner le creuset. Vous pourrez alors entrer en contact avec Illidan dans le Nant distordu.','','','','','','','21287'),
('36939','ptBR','O Sangue da Aniquilao','Recolha o Sangue de Malinoth.','Temos que fazer contato com o esprito de Lorde Illidan. Mas para isso precisamos de algo poderoso o bastante para energizar o crisol etreo. Eu sei o qu.\n\nUm senhor do fosso chamado Malinoth dominou uma caverna prxima. Se ns obtivermos seu sangue, voc poder us-lo para energizar o crisol. Ento voc poder fazer contato com Illidan na Espiral Etrea.','','','','','','','21287'),
('36949','enUS','Twisting in the Nether','Use Malinoth\'s Blood with the Nether Crucible to cast yourself into the Twisting Nether.','Quickly, $n. Pour the pit lord\'s blood into the crucible and make contact with Illidan\'s spirit.\n\nFind out everything you can. If we\'re to defeat the Legion, we must rescue Lord Illidan.','','','','','','','21491'),
('37258','enUS','The Forest God\'s Proposal','Witness Prince Farondis\' memory from the past.','I remember now. I was walking through my gardens, when I was visited by...$b$b<Farondis pauses.>$b$b...actually, it\'s easier if I show you, rather than explaining the whole thing.','','','','','','','21491'),
('37529','enUS','Golk\'s Lockbox','Obtain Golk\'s Key to open Golk\'s Lockbox.','You lucky.$b$bYou can just break chain and walk out of cave.$b$bGolk get no chain. Golk just get teleported in by naga and get stuck if try to get out.$b$bNaga take Golk treasure box key. Golk not getting out any time soon. You want Golk treasure? You can have it.','','','','','','','21491'),
