('40825','enUS','Arcano-Plasm','Collect 20 Arcano-Plasms from Arcano Pools or from dead Arcano Slimes in the Arcano Caverns.','You got time to give a goblin a hand? Good, thought so.$B$BI was flying my rocket and taking readings of this ley line, you see. Only I wasn\'t keeping an eye on my fuel reserves. Long story short, I ran out of gas.$B$BI set it down safely and all, but I don\'t have enough fuel to get me outta here. There\'s a nearby cave filled with Arcano-Plasm, which I can use to fuel my rocket. Wanna get some for me?$B$BOh yeah, you\'ll need this here Arcano-Drano to extract it.','','','','','','','21491'),
('40827','enUS','Clearing the Tunnels','Kill 8 Feeble Husks in the Arcano Caverns.','Before I went down, I was tracing the nearby ley line. Turns out, it goes right by the nearby caves.$B$BI\'d like to get down there for a closer look, but that ley line is attracting every withered from here to Azsuna.$B$BBut hey, you look like a strong $r. I bet you\'d have no problem clearing them out of there. It\'s just like trying to clear rats out of a sewer.$B$BWell, sort of.','','','','','','','21491'),
('40828','enUS','Fuel Transfer Worker','Retrieve FTW-001 from the Arcano Caverns.','I\'m no dummy, $n. I let my brains do the work for me. When I landed, I sent in my personal Fuel Transfer Worker to gather up the Arcano-Plasm.$B$BI call it the FTW-001. Great name, right? Well anyway, the darn thing never came back with my Arcano-Plasm.$B$BI ain\'t about to go chasing after it with all of those withered things running about.$B$BIf you come across the FTW-001, would ya let me know? I\'ll even throw in a few coins for your trouble.','','','','','','','21491'),
