('42981','enUS','Pure Water','Collect 10 Pure Water from naga and water elementals in the Eye of Azshara dungeon.','I may have discovered the key to restoring the pillar\'s magical energy.$B$BFirst, we will require a great deal of Pure Water. It is not easy to find, however I have heard that the naga in the Eye of Azshara are known to carry large quantities of this concentrated essence.$b$bIt will be not be easy, but if you can collect enough of the essence, we may be able to restore the pillar.','','','','','','Return to Elementalist Janai at the Heart of Azeroth.','21491'),
('43263','enUS','Growing Power','Use the Soul Forge to imbue your artifact, then speak with Highlord Darion Mograine.','The bond between you and your weapon has grown stronger, Deathlord. The time has come for you to direct the flow of power within your artifact.$b$bReturn to Acherus and speak with me when you have made your choice.','','Return to Acherus.','Highlord Darion Mograine','','','','21491'),
('43316','deDE','Nur mit Einladung','Bringt Ly\'leth Lunastre die handschriftliche Einladung.','While you were keeping His Highness busy, I found something of interest to Ly\'leth and the others.\n\n<Arluin dangles a colorful, elaborately decorated scroll in front of you.>\n\nIt is an invitation. To a party. A party which all of the Suramar nobility will be attending.\n\nNot least on the guest list is Grand Magistrix Elisande herself.\n\nIf you are thinking what I am thinking, then you would agree that Ly\'leth needs to know about this.\n\nImmediately.','','','','','','','21737'),
('43316','esES','Solo con invitacin','Llvale a Ly\'leth Lunastre la invitacin escrita a mano.','While you were keeping His Highness busy, I found something of interest to Ly\'leth and the others.\n\n<Arluin dangles a colorful, elaborately decorated scroll in front of you.>\n\nIt is an invitation. To a party. A party which all of the Suramar nobility will be attending.\n\nNot least on the guest list is Grand Magistrix Elisande herself.\n\nIf you are thinking what I am thinking, then you would agree that Ly\'leth needs to know about this.\n\nImmediately.','','','','','','','21737'),
('43316','frFR','Sur invitation uniquement','Apportez lInvitation manuscrite  Lyleth Lunastre.','While you were keeping His Highness busy, I found something of interest to Ly\'leth and the others.\n\n<Arluin dangles a colorful, elaborately decorated scroll in front of you.>\n\nIt is an invitation. To a party. A party which all of the Suramar nobility will be attending.\n\nNot least on the guest list is Grand Magistrix Elisande herself.\n\nIf you are thinking what I am thinking, then you would agree that Ly\'leth needs to know about this.\n\nImmediately.','','','','','','','21737'),
('43316','ptBR','S para convidados','Leve o Convite Feito a Mo para Ly\'leth Lunastre.','Enquanto voc mantinha sua Majestade ocupado, eu descobri algo do interesse de Ly\'leth e dos outros.\n\n<Arluin balana um pergaminho colorido elaboradamente decorado na sua frente.>\n\n um convite. Para uma festa. Uma festa onde toda a nobreza de Suramar estar presente.\n\nNingum menos que a Gr-magistra Elisande est na lista de convidados.\n\nSe est pensando o que eu estou pensando, ento voc deve concordar que Ly\'leth deve saber sobre isso.\n\nImediatamente.','','','','','','','21737'),
('43367','deDE','Feenstaub','Bringt Funkelchen $1oa Einheiten Arkhana. Arkhana wird durch Verzauberkunst erzeugt.','$GMein Freund:Meine Liebe,, Ihr habt so viel fr Funkelchen getan, aber es bleibt noch so viel mehr zu tun.$B$BIch habe hart daran gearbeitet, den Hain wiederherzustellen, doch meine Magie ist jetzt erschpft.$B$B<Funkelchens Magen knurrt laut.>$B$BOhne Magie kann ich nicht weitermachen. Die Verzauberer Eures Volks verwenden einen magischen Staub, der mich schnell wieder strken kann.$B$BWenn Ihr mir welchen bringt, geht es viel schneller voran!','','','','','','','21737'),
('43367','enUS','Pixie Dust','Bring $1oa Arkhana to Brightwing. Arkhana is obtained through the enchanting profession.','Friend, you have done so much for Brightwing, but there is still so much more to do.$B$BI\'ve been working so hard to restore the grove, but my magic is drained.$B$B<Brightwing\'s stomach grumbles loudly.>$B$BWithout magic, my work cannot continue. The enchanters of your people use a magical dust that can revitalize me quickly.$B$BIf you bring me some, I can work much faster!','','','','','','Return to Brightwing at the Emerald Dreamway.','21491'),
('43367','esES','Polvo de duendecillo','Lleva $1oa arkhana a Alasol. La arkhana se consigue mediante la profesin Encantamiento.','$GAmigo:Amiga,, has hecho mucho por Alasol, pero an queda mucho ms por hacer.$B$BHe trabajado duro para restaurar la arboleda, pero mi magia se ha secado.$B$B<A Alasol le suenan las tripas.>$B$BSin magia, mi trabajo no puede continuar. Los encantadores de tu gente usan un polvo mgico que puede revitalizarme enseguida.$B$BSi me traes un poco, podr trabajar mucho ms rpido!','','','','','','','21737'),
('43367','frFR','Poudre de perlimpinpin','Apportez $1oaunits dArkhana  Luisaile. Seuls les enchanteurs de mtier peuvent en obtenir.','$gAmi:Amie,, vous avez dj beaucoup aid Luisaile, mais il reste encore tellement  faire.$B$BJe travaille dur pour faire revivre le bosquet, mais ma magie est puise.$B$B<Lestomac de Luisaile gargouille bruyamment.>$B$BSans magie, je ne peux pas continuer. Heureusement, les enchanteurs de votre peuple utilisent une poudre magique qui me redonnera un bon coup de fouet en un rien de temps.$B$BSi vous men apportez, je pourrai travailler bien plus vite!','','','','','','','21737'),
('43367','ptBR','P de duente','Leve $1oa Arkhanas para Asaluz. Arkhana  obtida atravs da profisso de encantamento.','$GAmigo:Amiga,, voc fez tanto pela Asaluz, mas ainda h muito a se fazer.$B$BEu venho trabalhado tanto para restaurar o bosque, mas minha magia est drenada.$B$B<O estmago de Asaluz ronca alto.>$B$BSem magia, no posso continuar meu trabalho. Os encantadores do seu povo usam p mgico que pode me revitalizar rapidamente.$B$BSe voc me trouxer um pouco, eu posso trabalhar muito mais rpido!','','','','','','','21737'),
('43439','enUS','A Second Weapon','Give 300 Order Resources to Meryl to push forward research on other artifacts.','I see the Legion hasn\'t taken a bite out of you yet. It seems like that weapon is working out quite well.\n\nOur researches and scryers have been keeping a wary eye out on the other ancient weapons out there, mostly to make sure they don\'t fall into the hands of the Legion. But we could seek another to wield if you see fit.\n\nIn the meantime, the researchers are in desperate need of more resources. If you find enough to spare, I will see to it that they go to the right place.','','','','','','','21491'),
('43466','deDE','Verborgene Geschichte','Use Old Filmaff\'s notes to locate and recover the 4 ancient tomes for Edirah\'s research.','Alte Knochen eignen sich nicht gut fr harte Arbeit, aber im Laufe der Zeit lernt man zumindest, Muskelkraft durch Umsichtigkeit zu ersetzen... <Schnauft.> ...einen Teil davon zumindest.\n\nEdirah da drben hat hart an der Erforschung Eurer Waffe gearbeitet. Allerdings hat sie keine groen Fortschritte erzielen knnen, weil es ihr an den richtigen Materialien mangelt.\n\nEs gibt da ein paar Folianten, an die man nicht so leicht herankommt, und damit... <Hustet.> ...knnte sie ihre Forschungen etwas hurtiger vorantreiben.\n\nHier, ich gebe Euch eine Liste.','','','','','','','21737'),
('43466','enUS','Building on the Knowledge of Our Elders','Recover the 4 ancient conpendiums requested by your head researcher.','Greetings to you, $n.\n\nWe\'ve made great strides in uncovering knowledge about your weapon, but if we truly want to learn what it\'s capable of, we need to get our hands some texts that are... let\'s just say they\'re hard to come by.\n\nI can\'t emphasize enough how important this research will be to unlocking the remaining power within your weapon. If you can bring these tomes back to me, I promise you it will be well worth the effort.','','','','','','','21491'),
('43466','esES','Historia secreta','Use Old Filmaff\'s notes to locate and recover the 4 ancient tomes for Edirah\'s research.','Unos huesos viejos no son lo mejor para el trabajo duro, pero, con el tiempo, la sabidura compensa lo que te falta de msculo... <resopla>... Al menos un poquito.\n\nEdirah se ha estado matando para investigar esa arma tuya y algunos progresos ha hecho, pero le faltan los materiales adecuados.\n\nPodra decirte algunos tomos difciles de conseguir, eso s que podran... <tose>... que podran hacer avanzar un tanto su investigacin.\n\nMira, te har una lista.','','','','','','','21737'),
('43466','frFR','Histoire secrte','Use Old Filmaff\'s notes to locate and recover the 4 ancient tomes for Edirah\'s research.','Mes vieux os ne me permettent gure plus de matteler aux tches physiques, mais au fil du temps, la sagesse peut pallier le manque de force <Respire difficilement> du moins en partie.\n\nEdirah, que vous voyez l-bas, a effectu de longues et fastidieuses recherches sur votre arme. Elle a mme ralis quelques petits progrs ici et l, mais elle ne dispose pas des matriaux adquats.\n\nJe pourrais vous indiquer quelques livres, qui ne sont pas simples  obtenir, mais qui <Tousse> pourraient faire avancer les choses.\n\nTenez, voici la liste.','','','','','','','21737'),
('43466','ptBR','Histria escondida','Use Old Filmaff\'s notes to locate and recover the 4 ancient tomes for Edirah\'s research.','Ossos velhos no so bons para trabalhos pesados, mas com o tempo, a sabedoria compensa a falta de msculos... <Chiado>... ao menos em parte.\n\nA Edirah ali tem se matado de pesquisar aquela sua arma, tendo algum progresso aqui e ali, mas ela precisa dos materiais certos.\n\nH alguns tomos que eu posso apontar, saiba que no so fceis de se conseguir, mas que... <Tosse>... ajudariam a avanar a pesquisa um pouco.\n\nAqui, vou lhe dar uma lista.','','','','','','','21737'),
('43816','deDE','Verborgene Geschichte','Use Illiana Dreadmoore\'s notes to locate and recover the 4 ancient tomes she needs to begin research on your artifact.','Jeder Todesritter, der etwas auf sich hlt, kennt die Waffen, die er fhrt, als ob er mit ihnen geboren worden wre. Doch Ihr tragt jetzt eine Waffe, die lter ist als jede andere hier in dieser Halle.\n\nWenn Ihr wirklich ihre ganze Kraft freisetzen wollt, dann mssen wir mehr darber lernen. Forschung ist keine ruhmreiche Aufgabe und ist auf jeden Fall der Hand des Lichknigs unwrdig. Ich werde das fr Euch bernehmen.\n\nWenn ich mit der Forschung beginnen soll, brauche ich eine ganze Reihe uralter Folianten. Es ist womglich schwierig, sie zu beschaffen. Ich gebe Euch meine Aufzeichnungen zur Untersttzung bei der Suche.','','','','','','','21737'),
('43816','enUS','Hidden History','Use Illiana Dreadmoore\'s notes to locate and recover the 4 ancient tomes she needs to begin research on your artifact.','Any death knight worth their salt knows the weapon they wield as if they were born with it.  But you now carry a weapon older than any in this hall.\n\nIf we truly want to unlock all of its potential, we need to learn more about it. Research is not a glorious task, and is certainly unworthy of the Hand of the Lich King. I will do this for you.\n\nIf I am to get started, I need a series of ancient tomes to begin my research. They may be hard to procure. I\'ll give you my notes to help you find them.','','','','','','','21737'),
('43816','esES','Historia secreta','Use Illiana Dreadmoore\'s notes to locate and recover the 4 ancient tomes she needs to begin research on your artifact.','Cualquier caballero de la Muerte que se precie conoce su arma como si hubiera nacido con ella. Pero t ahora blandes un arma ms antigua que cualquiera de esta sala.\n\nSi de verdad queremos desbloquear todo su potencial, debemos averiguar ms al respecto. La investigacin no es una tarea gloriosa y es, desde luego, indigna de la Mano del Rey Exnime. Lo har por ti.\n\nPara poder empezar mi investigacin necesitar una serie de tomos antiguos. Pueden ser difciles de conseguir. Te dar mis notas para ayudarte a encontrarlos.','','','','','','','21737'),
('43816','frFR','Histoire secrte','Use Illiana Dreadmoore\'s notes to locate and recover the 4 ancient tomes she needs to begin research on your artifact.','Tout chasseur de dmons qui se respecte connat son arme comme si elle faisait partie de sa personne. Larme que vous brandissez est plus ancienne que toutes celles se trouvant en ces lieux.\n\nSi nous voulons vraiment librer son plein potentiel, il nous faut apprendre  la connatre. Ces recherches sont une tche ingrate, bien indigne de la Main du roi-liche. Cest pourquoi je vous propose de men occuper  votre place.\n\nToutefois, jai besoin dune srie danciens grimoires pour entamer mes recherches. Ils ne seront pas faciles  dnicher, mais je vais vous confier mes notes pour vous orienter dans votre qute.','','','','','','','21737'),
('43816','ptBR','Histria escondida','Use Illiana Dreadmoore\'s notes to locate and recover the 4 ancient tomes she needs to begin research on your artifact.','Qualquer cavaleiro da morte iniciante conhece a arma que empunha como se tivesse nascido com ela. S que agora voc porta uma arma mais antiga que qualquer uma neste salo.\n\nSe realmente quisermos liberar todo o potencial dela, temos que conhec-la melhor. A pesquisa no  uma tarefa gloriosa, e  certamente indigna da Mo do Lich Rei. Eu cuidarei dela para voc.\n\nPara comear minha pesquisa, preciso de tomos antigos, que podem ser difceis de obter. Eu lhe darei minhas anotaes para ajudar na busca.','','','','','','','21737'),
('43817','deDE','Verborgene Geschichte','Use Vehu\'s notes to locate and recover the 4 ancient tomes he needs to begin research on your artifact.','Ein Dmonenjger ist nichts ohne Klingen, mit denen er in Fleisch schneiden kann. Doch die Klingen, die Ihr dort fhrt, sind lter als Ihr... und besitzen eine Macht, die wir selbst noch nicht verstehen.\n\nWenn Ihr wirklich ihre ganze Kraft freisetzen wollt, dann mssen wir mehr darber lernen. Forschung ist keine ruhmreiche Aufgabe und ist auf jeden Fall der Hand von Illidan unwrdig. Ich werde das fr Euch bernehmen.\n\nWenn ich mit der Forschung beginnen soll, brauche ich eine ganze Reihe uralter Folianten. Es ist womglich schwierig, sie zu beschaffen. Ich gebe Euch meine Aufzeichnungen zur Untersttzung bei der Suche.','','','','','','','21737'),
('43817','enUS','Hidden History','Use Vehu\'s notes to locate and recover the 4 ancient tomes he needs to begin research on your artifact.','A demon hunter is nothing without blades with which to cut flesh. Yet those you wield are older than even you... and have power we don\'t understand yet.\n\nIf you truly want to unlock all of their potential, we need to learn more about them. Research is not a glorious task, and is certainly unworthy of the Hand of Illidan. I will do this for you.\n\nIf I am to get started, I need a series of ancient tomes to begin my research. They may be hard to procure. I\'ll give you my notes to help you find them.','','','','','','','21737'),
('43817','esES','Historia secreta','Use Vehu\'s notes to locate and recover the 4 ancient tomes he needs to begin research on your artifact.','Un cazador de demonios no es nada sin unas hojas con las que cortar carne. Pero las que t empuas son ms viejas incluso que t... y tienen un poder que an no entiendes.\n\nSi de verdad quieres desbloquear todo su potencial, necesitamos saber ms al respecto. La investigacin no es una tarea gloriosa y es, desde luego, indigna de la Mano de Illidan. Lo har por ti.\n\nPara poder empezar mi investigacin necesitar una serie de tomos antiguos. Pueden ser difciles de conseguir. Te dar mis notas para ayudarte a encontrarlos.','','','','','','','21737'),
('43817','frFR','Histoire secrte','Use Vehu\'s notes to locate and recover the 4 ancient tomes he needs to begin research on your artifact.','Sans lames pour trancher la chair, un chasseur de dmons nest rien. Les armes que vous brandissez sont plus anciennes que vous et pourtant, nous les comprenons  peine.\n\nSi vous voulez vraiment librer leur plein potentiel, il nous faut apprendre  les connatre. Ces recherches sont une tche ingrate, bien indigne de la Main dIllidan. Cest pourquoi je vous propose de men occuper  votre place.\n\nToutefois, jai besoin dune srie danciens grimoires pour entamer mes recherches. Ils ne seront pas faciles  dnicher, mais je vais vous confier mes notes pour vous orienter dans votre qute.','','','','','','','21737'),
