('43824','enUS','Hidden History','Use Gorma\'s notes to locate and recover the 4 ancient tomes she needs to begin research on your artifact.','You have a weapon both ancient and powerful. We know stories of it, but little about its origins.\n\nIf we truly want to unlock all of its potential, we need to learn more about it. The winds can help us with this, but we need to know what to ask.\n\nI know of a few books that will give me the right place to start. They may be hard to get your hands on, but they\'ll be worth it. I\'ll give you my notes to help you find them.','','','','','','','21737'),
('43824','esES','Historia secreta','Use Gorma\'s notes to locate and recover the 4 ancient tomes she needs to begin research on your artifact.','Tienes un arma antigua y poderosa. Conocemos historias al respecto, pero poca cosa sobre sus orgenes.\n\nSi realmente queremos acceder a todo su potencial, debemos averiguar ms sobre ella. Los vientos pueden ayudarnos, pero debemos saber qu preguntarles.\n\nS de unos cuantos libros que me dirn por dnde empezar. Pueden ser difciles de conseguir, pero valdrn la pena. Te dar mis notas para ayudarte a encontrarlos.','','','','','','','21737'),
('43824','frFR','Histoire secrte','Use Gorma\'s notes to locate and recover the 4 ancient tomes she needs to begin research on your artifact.','Votre arme est aussi ancienne que puissante. Nous connaissons les lgendes qui lui sont associes, mais nous ignorons tout de ses origines.\n\nSi nous voulons librer son plein potentiel, il nous faut apprendre  la connatre. Les vents peuvent nous y aider, mais encore faut-il leur poser les bonnes questions.\n\nJai pens  certains livres susceptibles de me fournir un bon point de dpart. Vous aurez sans doute du mal  vous les procurer, mais le jeu en vaut la chandelle. Je vais vous confier mes notes pour orienter vos recherches.','','','','','','','21737'),
('43824','ptBR','Histria escondida','Use Gorma\'s notes to locate and recover the 4 ancient tomes she needs to begin research on your artifact.','Voc tem uma arma to antiga quanto poderosa. Conhecemos algumas histrias, mas pouco sabemos da origem dela.\n\nSe realmente quisermos liberar todo o potencial da arma, temos que conhec-la melhor. Os ventos podem nos ajudar, mas precisamos saber o que perguntar.\n\nSei de alguns livros que serviro de ponto de partida. Podem ser muito difceis de obter, mas valero a pena. Eu lhe darei minhas anotaes para ajudar na busca.','','','','','','','21737'),
('43825','deDE','Verborgene Geschichte','Use Mile\'s notes to locate and recover the 4 ancient tomes he needs to begin research on your artifact.','Ihr seid im Besitz einer uralten und mchtigen Waffe, und doch verstehen wir kaum etwas von ihr.\n\nWenn wir wirklich ihr gesamtes Potential freisetzen wollen, mssen wir mehr darber erfahren. Das ist etwas, das ich fr Euch erledigen kann.\n\nBevor ich allerdings mit meiner Forschung beginnen kann, brauche ich eine ganze Reihe uralter Folianten. Es ist womglich schwierig, sie zu beschaffen. Ich gebe Euch meine Aufzeichnungen zur Untersttzung bei der Suche.','','','','','','','21737'),
('43825','enUS','Hidden History','Use Mile\'s notes to locate and recover the 4 ancient tomes he needs to begin research on your artifact.','You have a weapon both ancient and powerful. And yet, we barely understand it.\n\nIf we truly want to unlock all of its potential, we need to learn more about it. That is a thing that I can do for you.\n\nBefore I can get started though, I need a series of ancient tomes to begin my research. They may be hard to procure. I\'ll give you my notes to help you find them.','','','','','','','21737'),
('43825','esES','Historia secreta','Use Mile\'s notes to locate and recover the 4 ancient tomes he needs to begin research on your artifact.','Tienes un arma antigua y poderosa. Y aun as, apenas la entendemos.\n\nSi de verdad queremos acceder a todo su potencial, debemos averiguar ms al respecto. Es algo que puedo hacer por ti.\n\nPero para poder comenzar mi investigacin necesito una serie de tomos. Pueden ser difciles de conseguir. Te dar mis notas para ayudarte a encontrarlos.','','','','','','','21737'),
('43825','frFR','Histoire secrte','Use Mile\'s notes to locate and recover the 4 ancient tomes he needs to begin research on your artifact.','Votre arme est aussi puissante quancienne, et pourtant, nous la comprenons  peine.\n\nSi nous voulons librer son plein potentiel, il nous faut apprendre  la connatre. Et je suis prt  vous y aider.\n\nToutefois, avant de commencer, jai besoin dune srie danciens grimoires pour entamer mes recherches. Ils ne seront pas faciles  dnicher, mais je vais vous confier mes notes pour vous orienter dans votre qute.','','','','','','','21737'),
('43825','ptBR','Histria escondida','Use Mile\'s notes to locate and recover the 4 ancient tomes he needs to begin research on your artifact.','Voc tem uma arma to antiga quanto poderosa. Entretanto, mal a entendemos.\n\nSe realmente quisermos liberar todo o potencial dela, temos que conhec-la melhor.  algo que posso fazer por voc.\n\nPara comear minha pesquisa, preciso de tomos antigos, que podem ser difceis de obter. Aqui esto minhas anotaes para ajudar na busca.','','','','','','','21737'),
('43937','deDE','Zuflucht suchen','Schliet den Handlungsstrang \"Einbruch der Nacht\" in Suramar ab und trefft dann Erzmagier Kalec in Shal\'Aran.','Die Nachtschtigen in Suramar gehrten frher zu den Nachtgeborenen, doch ihre einstigen Brder verbannten sie und verwehrten ihnen den Zugang zum Nachtbrunnen.$B$BIch glaube, sie knnten bei unserer Suche wertvolle Verbndete sein, wenn Ihr sie auf unsere Seite ziehen knnt. Ich wei nur, dass sie irgendwo in Suramar untergetaucht sind.$B$BWenn Ihr die Nachtschtigen davon berzeugen knnt, uns zu helfen, knnten sie der Mondwache und uns womglich Zuflucht direkt vor der Nase der Legion bieten.','','','','','','','24367'),
('43937','enUS','Seeking Refuge','Complete the \"Nightfall\" storyline in Suramar, then meet Archmage Kalec in Shal\'Aran.','The Nightfallen in Suramar were once a part of the Nightborne, but have been exiled by their former brethren and cut off from the Nightwell.$B$BI believe they could be valuable allies in our quest if you can turn them to our side. I know only that they have gone into hiding somewhere in Suramar.$B$BIf you can convince the Nightfallen to aid us, they may be able to offer the Moon Guard and us both refuge right under the Legion\'s nose.','','','','','','','24367'),
('43937','esES','Buscar refugio','Completa la trama de \"Ocaso\" en Suramar y luego renete con el archimago Kalec en Shal\'Aran.','Los Cados de la Noche de Suramar fueron antao parte de los Nocheterna, pero sus antiguos hermanos los desterraron y aislaron de la Fuente de la Noche.$B$BCreo que pueden ser unos aliados muy valiosos para nuestra misin si puedes ponerlos de nuestra parte. Solo s que se han escondido en algn lugar de Suramar.$B$BSi logras convencer a los Cados de la Noche de que nos ayuden, quizs puedan ofrecernos refugio a nosotros y a la Guardia Lunar ante las narices de la Legin.','','','','','','','24367'),
('43937','esMX','Buscando refugio','Completa la trama \"Ocaso\" en Suramar y luego encuentra al Archimago Kalec en Shal\'Aran.','Los Cados de la Noche en Suramar solan ser parte de los nato nocturnos, pero fueron exiliados por sus antiguos hermanos y se les prohibi acceso a la Fuente de la Noche.$B$BCreo que podran ser valiosos aliados para nuestra misin si logramos hacer que se unan a nosotros. Solo s que se fueron a esconder a Suramar.$B$BSi puedes convencer a los nato nocturnos para que nos ayuden, es probable que puedan ofrecerle a la Guardia lunar y a nosotros refugio justo bajo las narices de la Legin.','','','','','','','24367'),
('43937','frFR','Demande dasile','Achevez la suite de qutes Tombe-nuit  Suramar, puis allez voir lArchimage Kalec  ShalAran.','Autrefois Sacrenuit, les Souffrenuit de Suramar ont t exils par leurs anciens frres et coups du Puits de la nuit.$B$BJe pense quils feraient dexcellents allis dans notre qute si vous parvenez  les convaincre de nous aider. Ils se cachent quelque part  Suramar, mais je nen sais pas plus, malheureusement.$B$BPersuadez-les de nous aider et ils pourraient bien fournir,  la garde de la Lune comme  nos troupes, un abri au nez et  la barbe de la Lgion.','','','','','','','24367'),
('43937','ptBR','Em busca de refgio','Conclua a histria \"Anoitecer\" em Suramar, e ento encontre-se com o Arquimago Kalec em Shal\'Aran.','Os noctvoros em Suramar eram parte dos Filhos da Noite, mas foram exilados por seus antigos irmos e removidos da Nascente da Noite.$B$BAcredito que eles seriam aliados valiosos na nossa misso, se voc puder convenc-los. Sei apenas que eles se esconderam em algum lugar de Suramar.$B$BSe voc puder convencer os Noctvoros para que eles nos ajudem, eles podem nos oferecer a Guarda da Lua e conseguiremos refgio bem debaixo dos olhos da Legio.','','','','','','','24367'),
('44091','deDE','Needs of the Many','Seek out the Kirin Tor mages in Orgrimmar and travel to Dalaran.','You\'ve seen that the Legion is everywhere. Even with the Illidari as your allies, we are at a great disadvantage.$b$bWe need an edge against the Legion... something to send them back to the Nether.$b$bWe have heard that Dalaran will be the focal point of our campaign. I suggest you go there. You must do anything necessary to become stronger. ANYTHING.$b$bI have seen Kirin Tor mages near Grommash Hold. They can send you to Dalaran.$b$bGo. Take revenge upon the Legion!','','','','','','','21737'),
